<li>Miller, James, L., "Measures of Wisdom: The Cosmic Dance in Classical and Christian Antiquity", <a href="/wiki/University_of_Toronto_Press" title="University of Toronto Press">University of Toronto Press</a>, 1986. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0802025536" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-8020-2553-6</a></li>
<li>Velasquez, Susan McNeal, "Beyond Intellect: Journey Into the Wisdom of Your Intuitive Mind", Row Your Boat Press, 2007. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780979641008" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-0-9796410-0-8</a></li>
